para_trans: Government Order No: MVD 0624 / P.No.262 / PARI-4
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Government Orders - Appointment of transfers and postings of Maharashtra Government employees in the discharge of government duties -
Substitution under the provisions of sections 4 (4) (two) and 4 (5) of the Prevention of Delay Act, 2005.
Officers of the Sub-Regional Transport Officer cadre with the approval of the authority competent to do so.
As per the request, his name is mentioned in front of Column No. Being transferred to the position indicated in section 4

The Controlling Officer concerned shall relieve the said transferred officers from their present office with immediate effect and the officers concerned shall be posted at the place of the new posting within such period as may be prescribed.
The report of joining and assuming office should be submitted to the government through the Transport Commissioner's office.
The Government Order is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
